OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 11 MAR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1992FThe Nine o'Clock News (BBC One)
OL,7,Fis replaced by Nine o'Clock News and
OL,8,FCampaign Report (until 9th April 1992).
OL,9,FMartyn Lewis (or Michael Buerk),
OL,10,Falongside Peter Snow presented the
OL,11,Flatest election campaign news. Jill
OL,12,FDando brought us the rest of the day's
OL,13,Fnews. The studio set featured a blue
OL,14,Fbackground and two desks. During the
OL,15,Fcampaign, the daytime news summaries
OL,16,Fwere also presented from a set with a
OL,17,Fblue background.
OL,18,
OL,19,CG1996FThe final episode of Our Friends
OL,20,Fin the North airs on BBC Two.
